<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Adults-Only Notice – LumenNyx Studios</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
</head>
<body class="auth-page">
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand-link">
        <span class="brand-mark">
          <img src="/img/lumennyx-mark.png" alt="LumenNyx logo">
        </span>
        <span class="brand-text">LUMENNYX STUDIOS</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/" class="active">Home</a>
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
        <a href="/2257">2257</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-wrapper">
    <section class="auth-card">
      <h2>Adults-Only Private Portal</h2>
      <p class="auth-subtext">
        This is a private model and studio collaborator portal for
        <strong>LumenNyx Studios</strong>, an independent adult production
        studio based near Wallkill, NY (Hudson Valley region).
      </p>

      <div class="release-box" style="margin-bottom: 1.1rem;">
        <div class="release-text">
          <p>To continue, you must confirm that:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>You are at least <strong>18 years old</strong> (or 21+ where required by local law).</li>
            <li>You understand this portal relates to <strong>adult content production</strong>, not escorting or prostitution.</li>
            <li>You are accessing this portal from a place where viewing / working with adult-content-related material is <strong>legal</strong>.</li>
            <li>You will keep login details private and will not allow anyone under 18 to view or use this portal.</li>
          </ul>

          <p class="field-help" style="margin-top: 0.6rem;">
            This portal is <strong>not a public porn site</strong>. It is for models, talent, and studio staff
            to manage paperwork, IDs, releases, and scene logistics. Nothing here is individualized legal advice.
            For model onboarding, contact <strong>models@lumennyxstudios.com</strong>. For general support, contact
            <strong>support@lumennyxstudios.com</strong>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error) { %>
        <div class="alert error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <form action="/age-check" method="POST" class="auth-form">
        <input type="hidden" name="age_confirm" value="yes" />
        <button type="submit" class="btn primary" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 0.6rem;">
          I am 18 or older and I agree
        </button>
      </form>

      <button
        type="button"
        class="btn secondary"
        style="width: 100%; margin-top: 0.2rem;"
        onclick="window.location.href='https://www.google.com';"
      >
        I am under 18 / Take me away
      </button>

      <p class="auth-note">
        By clicking “I am 18 or older and I agree”, you confirm that your statements are true and that you understand
        this is a professional production portal. Misrepresentation may violate local or federal law.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
